1
00:01:03,710 --> 00:01:05,880
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,250 --> 00:01:09,870
[Episode 2]

3
00:01:11,950 --> 00:01:12,560
Li,

4
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:14,280
don't be nervous
on your first visit to the palace.

5
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:15,710
I'm here with you. Don't be afraid.

6
00:01:15,710 --> 00:01:16,950
This way, please.

7
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:23,280
I'll escort you only this far.

8
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:24,590
Please.

9
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:29,150
It's been a few days.

10
00:01:29,150 --> 00:01:31,480
Consort Ling looks more radiant than ever.

11
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:32,479
Indeed.

12
00:01:35,590 --> 00:01:37,120
Where did this uncouth girl come from?

13
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:37,170
You don't even know
how to bow before Consort Ling?

14
00:01:37,170 --> 00:01:39,580
[Consort Ling]

15
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,460
Greetings, Consort Ling.

16
00:01:43,509 --> 00:01:45,560
Li, quickly bow to Consort Ling.

17
00:01:48,070 --> 00:01:49,530
Greetings, Consort Ling.

18
00:01:50,479 --> 00:01:52,229
A girl really can't grow up

19
00:01:52,229 --> 00:01:53,890
without a mother's guidance.

20
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:54,759
Look at her.

21
00:01:54,759 --> 00:01:56,640
So completely ignorant
of proper etiquette.

22
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,870
The first wife died young.

23
00:01:57,870 --> 00:02:00,230
And her only daughter
knows nothing of manners.

24
00:02:00,230 --> 00:02:01,510
It's absolutely disgraceful.

25
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:03,590
Such a shame to the Jiang family.

26
00:02:03,590 --> 00:02:05,560
Looks like all that sage wisdom you read

27
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,280
went straight into a dog's gut.

28
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:09,150
You're so well-educated and reasonable.

29
00:02:09,150 --> 00:02:10,710
Then I suppose I read it

30
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:12,150
into your gut.

31
00:02:12,310 --> 00:02:12,870
You...

32
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:13,750
Li.

33
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,310
General Xun.

34
00:02:15,310 --> 00:02:16,960
The empress dowager favors you so much,

35
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:20,020
yet you allow this woman
to be so insolent in the palace?

36
00:02:20,310 --> 00:02:22,510
Li, quickly apologize to Consort Ling.

37
00:02:26,470 --> 00:02:28,190
Why should I apologize to you?

38
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:28,960
You...

39
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,000
You uncouth creature!

40
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,590
Guards! Take her away!

41
00:02:33,590 --> 00:02:36,400
His Majesty arrives!

42
00:02:50,150 --> 00:02:51,430
Your Majesty.

43
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:54,750
Your Majesty.

44
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:10,960
I heard the Grand Tutor's only daughter
entered the palace today.

45
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:13,630
I have heard quite a few rumors
about you, Miss Jiang.

46
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:15,190
Why does his voice sound so familiar?

47
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:16,360
They say you enjoy drinking,

48
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:19,590
especially the wine
from Wenxiang Pavilion.

49
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:22,030
Everyone may rise.

50
00:03:31,190 --> 00:03:32,079
Zhao?

51
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:36,750
I hope whenever
you think of me in the future,

52
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:40,079
you'll remember tonight.

53
00:03:40,870 --> 00:03:41,590
Li!

54
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,560
Li!

55
00:03:50,430 --> 00:03:51,160
By the way...

56
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:55,150
General Xun.

57
00:03:58,590 --> 00:04:00,710
I have a gift for you.

58
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,400
This is...

59
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:11,310
Reduced to ashes—

60
00:04:11,310 --> 00:04:13,520
no wonder you couldn't recognize him.

61
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,280
Ashes.

62
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,920
Your deputy commander
was lax in discipline

63
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:17,560
and embezzled military funds.

64
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,089
I've dealt with him for you.

65
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,870
Consider it my way of preserving
your reputation, General Xun.

66
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:24,310
What do you think, General Xun?

67
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:30,310
I thank Your Majesty.

68
00:04:30,310 --> 00:04:31,040
Report!

69
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,800
The empress dowager has issued an edict.

70
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:36,000
She summons General Xun and Miss Jiang.

71
00:04:37,870 --> 00:04:41,480
General Xun, I hope you will
behave yourself in the future.

72
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,870
Don't be like your subordinates

73
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:48,200
who touched what they shouldn't have.

74
00:04:58,780 --> 00:05:02,980
[Auspicious Mists of Grace and Peace]

75
00:05:07,630 --> 00:05:10,230
-Greetings, Aunt.
-Greetings, Your Majesty.

76
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:14,600
[Xuan Huaijin,
Empress Dowager of the Zhao State]

77
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:20,630
So this is
the Grand Tutor's only daughter?

78
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,360
Li.

79
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,750
Greetings, Your Majesty.

80
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,890
You truly are delicate and charming.

81
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:34,270
It wasn't in vain
that I issued this marriage decree.

82
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:37,500
Thank you for your kind words,
Your Majesty.

83
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:40,600
The Grand Tutor is a scholar.

84
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:44,310
I assume you understand that as a woman,

85
00:05:44,310 --> 00:05:46,600
you should do your best
to support your husband.

86
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:49,680
In the future, you must
control your words and actions.

87
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,870
Don't cause trouble

88
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:53,560
and burden Simo.

89
00:05:54,310 --> 00:05:55,360
Aunt is right.

90
00:05:55,510 --> 00:05:59,390
We will certainl
be in harmony as husband and wife

91
00:05:59,510 --> 00:06:01,510
and share all honors and hardships.

92
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:06,190
Enough. I am tired.

93
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:07,870
You may withdraw now.

94
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,120
Yes.

95
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,920
I didn't mean to, my lady.

96
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,070
It was an accident.

97
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:16,000
It's fine. It's just a small stain.

98
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:18,360
How improper to be dressed so untidily.

99
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,830
Take her to change her clothes.

100
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:20,600
Yes.

101
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,480
Simo,

102
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:28,070
stay and chat with me for a while.

103
00:06:33,190 --> 00:06:33,800
Yes.

104
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,800
Please wait here.

105
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:43,130
I'll go fetch new clothes
for you, my lady.

106
00:06:52,190 --> 00:06:53,600
This is...

107
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,630
How dare you

108
00:07:32,159 --> 00:07:35,480
enter my royal bathing chamber!

109
00:07:42,159 --> 00:07:44,159
I didn't know Your Majesty was here.

110
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:45,800
Please allow me to leave.

111
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:55,720
That day,

112
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,280
you said you were tired of me,

113
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,390
but from what I see now,

114
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,400
that doesn't seem to be the case.

115
00:08:03,310 --> 00:08:05,360
Mrs. Xun.

116
00:08:16,430 --> 00:08:19,310
I will soon marry General Xun.

117
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:21,360
Please conduct yourself
with dignity, Your Majesty.

118
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:23,430
Do not violate the propriety
between ruler and subject.

119
00:08:23,430 --> 00:08:25,390
The propriety between ruler and subject?

120
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:27,120
The Li I know

121
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:29,720
never cared about such social conventions.

122
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:31,160
Besides,

123
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:33,150
if I wanted to take you by force,

124
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:36,720
what could Xun Simo possibly do about it?

125
00:08:41,750 --> 00:08:42,549
What?

126
00:08:42,909 --> 00:08:44,790
Are you inviting me

127
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:47,440
to bathe with you?

128
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,120
Li!

129
00:08:50,910 --> 00:08:52,510
Are you in there, Li?

130
00:08:52,630 --> 00:08:55,870
General Xun seems quite anxious.

131
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:59,120
Perhaps I should let him in.

132
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:01,150
Li, I'm coming in.

133
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,200
Li!

134
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,550
Li!

135
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:06,240
Xun...

136
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:33,310
My lady, have some wine
to warm yourself up.

137
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:36,480
Xi'er, you're the best.

138
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,150
Of course.

139
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:40,960
I specially bought it
from Wenxiang Pavilion.

140
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,910
I've been keeping it warm
in the hot spring.

141
00:09:42,910 --> 00:09:45,170
Don't mention Wenxiang Pavilion again.

142
00:09:45,270 --> 00:09:46,440
This wine...

143
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:49,320
Don't buy it anymore.

144
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,440
Why?

145
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,600
Isn't this your favorite wine?

146
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:54,360
After you returned from the palace today,

147
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:56,030
you've been acting strange.

148
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:57,440
What happened?

149
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:02,080
Xi'er, you must trust me.

150
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:05,840
I'm keeping silent to protect you.

151
00:10:10,670 --> 00:10:12,030
All right then.

152
00:10:15,630 --> 00:10:16,430
Your Majesty,

153
00:10:16,550 --> 00:10:19,150
Miss Jiang is currently
engaged to Xun Simo.

154
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:22,750
From now on,
she'll probably be one of them.

155
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,120
In my humble opinion,

156
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:29,750
-we should take initiative...
-If she really wants to marry into

157
00:10:29,750 --> 00:10:31,270
the Xun family, then she is my enemy.

158
00:10:31,270 --> 00:10:31,910
I will

159
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,390
show no mercy.

160
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,030
Yes.

161
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,030
Also,

162
00:10:40,550 --> 00:10:42,320
if she leaves the Grand Tutor's Mansion,

163
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:44,720
I want to be the first
to know where she goes.

164
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:46,480
Yes.

165
00:10:48,790 --> 00:10:51,050
There are so many beauties in this world.

166
00:10:51,050 --> 00:10:53,080
I was merely playing with her,

167
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,960
just a brief affair.

168
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:04,670
Tell me. Who sent you?

169
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,630
It doesn't matter.

170
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:11,870
I have ways to make you talk.

171
00:11:22,500 --> 00:11:24,980
[Chunliu Garden]

172
00:11:28,130 --> 00:11:30,570
[Spiritual Sound of Stone]

173
00:11:50,730 --> 00:11:52,680
[Liu Yeqing, Jiang Li's Mother]

174
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:56,650
[Young Jiang Li]

175
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:00,630
Li, you left the Grand Tutor's Mansion
and came here with me.

176
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:01,960
Do you feel aggrieved?

177
00:12:02,030 --> 00:12:03,600
I don't feel aggrieved.

178
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:05,630
I hate Father's house too.

179
00:12:05,630 --> 00:12:07,630
I just want to stay with you, Mother.

180
00:12:08,550 --> 00:12:09,550
It's just that...

181
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,790
I feel it's unfair to you.

182
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:14,180
Why should you be the one to leave?

183
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:24,550
Having you by my side

184
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:26,750
is what I treasure most.

185
00:12:30,030 --> 00:12:30,840
Li.

186
00:12:31,550 --> 00:12:33,510
A woman with talent and virtue

187
00:12:33,750 --> 00:12:35,440
need not depend on a man.

188
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:37,480
This is the way to live in peace.

189
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,480
I believe that

190
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:41,510
compared to staying in

191
00:12:41,510 --> 00:12:43,840
that prison-like Grand Tutor's Mansion,

192
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:45,670
being with you and living freely

193
00:12:45,670 --> 00:12:47,200
is far more precious.

194
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,240
Isn't that right?

195
00:12:55,390 --> 00:12:56,200
Mother,

196
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:58,720
I hope your spirit in heaven

197
00:12:59,150 --> 00:13:00,670
will protect me.

198
00:13:07,670 --> 00:13:09,200
Your Majesty,

199
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:11,780
the men are waiting outside the city.

200
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:12,960
They're all skilled fighters

201
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:15,890
who will certainly complete
the task as you ordered.

202
00:13:17,150 --> 00:13:19,870
Make it clean. Leave no body.

203
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,910
We'll say the girl ran away,

204
00:13:23,390 --> 00:13:24,390
so I

205
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:27,440
can arrange another good match for Simo.

206
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:30,240
What about Grand Tutor Jiang?

207
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:32,270
Since his daugther
ran away from the wedding,

208
00:13:32,270 --> 00:13:34,530
he'll have to explain it to Simo himself.

209
00:13:34,870 --> 00:13:35,960
I understand.

210
00:13:40,790 --> 00:13:43,390
-Greetings, Your Majesty.
-Greetings, Aunt.

211
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:49,000
The resemblance is striking.

212
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:53,380
Why couldn't Simo fall for someone else?

213
00:13:54,390 --> 00:13:56,080
Why did it have to be her?
